                <h1>How to Change Call Background on iPhone: A Quick Guide</h1>
                <p>To change the call background on your iPhone, open the Contacts app and select a contact. Tap 'Edit' and then 'Edit' under the contact photo. Choose 'Take Photo' or 'Choose Photo' to add a new image. This will customize the background for calls from that contact. Save your changes to complete!</p>
